<div id="post-823" class="post-823 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-blog-nate-thayer category-humor category-kim-il-sung category-kim-jong-il category-kim-jong-un category-media category-nate-thayer category-north-korea category-north-korean-capitalism category-north-korean-government-control category-north-korean-propaganda category-propoganda tag-democratic-peoples-republic-of-korea tag-human-rights tag-humor tag-journalism tag-kim-jong-il tag-kim-jong-un tag-nate-thayer tag-north-korea tag-north-korea-sanctions-kim-jong-un tag-north-korean-propaganda-2">

	
	<h2 class="title"><a href="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/2013/01/26/frequent-flyers-guide-to-north-korean-air-a-review-of-worlds-only-one-star-airline/" rel="bookmark" title="Frequent Flyer’s Guide to North Korean Air: a Review of World’s Only One Star&nbsp;Airline">Frequent Flyer’s Guide to North Korean Air: a Review of World’s Only One Star&nbsp;Airline</a></h2>
	<a class="date" href="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/2013/01/26/frequent-flyers-guide-to-north-korean-air-a-review-of-worlds-only-one-star-airline/">
		<span class="day">26</span>
		<span class="month">Jan</span>
	</a>

	

	<div class="entry">
		<p><b>Frequent Flyer’s Guide to North Korean Air: <i>a Review of World’s Only One Star Airline</i></b></p>
<p><em><strong>By Nate Thayer</strong> </em></p>
<p>Air Koryo, North Korea’s official airline, is rated the world’s only one star air carrier. But it is improving. In August, Pyongyang’s promise of being global technological leaders achieved a key milestone, when the national airline announced it would offer online reservations with “convenient reservations day and night&#8221;.</p>
<p>The official airline of North Korea now allows international travelers to book one of their eight weekly international flights, which accommodate the global hubs between Pyongyang and Beijing, Pyongyang and Shenyang, China, or Pyongyang and Vladivostok.</p>
<p>Air Koryo says customers can purchase additional room for their “black box” or for their “fat”, according to the Air Koryo website, which is inexplicably down at the moment</p>
<p>There is a hitch though; the airline doesn’t accept credit cards, so one has to use PayPal.</p>
<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_824" style="width: 500px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/air-koryo-online-booking.jpg"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-824" data-attachment-id="824" data-permalink="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/2013/01/26/frequent-flyers-guide-to-north-korean-air-a-review-of-worlds-only-one-star-airline/air-koryo-online-booking/" data-orig-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/air-koryo-online-booking.jpg" data-orig-size="640,432" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-image-title="air-koryo-online-booking" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/air-koryo-online-booking.jpg?w=300" data-large-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/air-koryo-online-booking.jpg?w=490" class="size-full wp-image-824" alt="Air Koryo website for revolutionary new online bookings for reservations. Unfortunately they don't accept credit cards" src="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/air-koryo-online-booking.jpg?w=490&#038;h=330" width="490" height="330" srcset="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/air-koryo-online-booking.jpg?w=490&amp;h=330 490w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/air-koryo-online-booking.jpg?w=150&amp;h=101 150w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/air-koryo-online-booking.jpg?w=300&amp;h=203 300w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/air-koryo-online-booking.jpg 640w" sizes="(max-width: 490px) 100vw, 490px" /></a><p id="caption-attachment-824" class="wp-caption-text">Air Koryo website for revolutionary new online bookings for reservations. Unfortunately they don&#8217;t accept credit cards</p></div>
<p>Air Koryo offers scheduled flights from Pyongyang to Beijing and Shenyang in China and Vladivostok in Russia.</p>
<p>There are a number of independent air travel rating services that rate the service. Skytrax, a company that ranks global air transport gives Air Koryo the only airline on earth a one-star rating that represents &#8220;very poor quality performance&#8221;.</p>
<p><a href="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/airkoryo-620x410.png"><img data-attachment-id="825" data-permalink="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/2013/01/26/frequent-flyers-guide-to-north-korean-air-a-review-of-worlds-only-one-star-airline/airkoryo-620x410/" data-orig-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/airkoryo-620x410.png" data-orig-size="620,410" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-image-title="AirKoryo-620&#215;410" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/airkoryo-620x410.png?w=300" data-large-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/airkoryo-620x410.png?w=490" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-825" alt="AirKoryo-620x410" src="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/airkoryo-620x410.png?w=490&#038;h=324" width="490" height="324" srcset="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/airkoryo-620x410.png?w=490&amp;h=324 490w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/airkoryo-620x410.png?w=150&amp;h=99 150w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/airkoryo-620x410.png?w=300&amp;h=198 300w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/airkoryo-620x410.png 620w" sizes="(max-width: 490px) 100vw, 490px" /></a> <a href="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/air-koryo-is-not-quality-approved-and-has-1-star-general-ratings-almost-across-the-board-from-skytrax-jpg.gif"><img data-attachment-id="838" data-permalink="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/2013/01/26/frequent-flyers-guide-to-north-korean-air-a-review-of-worlds-only-one-star-airline/air-koryo-is-not-quality-approved-and-has-1-star-