<div id="post-810" class="post-810 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-free-speech-2 category-journalism category-journalistic-ethics category-kim-il-sung category-kim-jong-il category-kim-jong-un category-media category-nate-thayer category-north-korea category-north-korea-media category-north-korean-propaganda category-propoganda tag-democratic-peoples-republic-of-korea tag-journalism tag-khmer-rouge-and-north-korea-2 tag-kim-jong-il tag-kim-jong-un tag-media-ethics tag-nate-thayer tag-north-korea tag-north-korea-sanctions-kim-jong-un tag-north-korean-media tag-north-korean-propaganda-2">

	
	<h2 class="title"><a href="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/2013/01/24/north-korea-erupts-at-sordid-hackwork-by-rubbish-media-vows-a-dear-price-the-human-scum-and-mediawill-have-to-pay/" rel="bookmark" title="North Korea Erupts at &#8220;sordid hackwork by rubbish media&#8221;: Vows a &#8220;dear price the human scum and media&#8221;will &#8220;have to&nbsp;pay&#8221;">North Korea Erupts at &#8220;sordid hackwork by rubbish media&#8221;: Vows a &#8220;dear price the human scum and media&#8221;will &#8220;have to&nbsp;pay&#8221;</a></h2>
	<a class="date" href="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/2013/01/24/north-korea-erupts-at-sordid-hackwork-by-rubbish-media-vows-a-dear-price-the-human-scum-and-mediawill-have-to-pay/">
		<span class="day">24</span>
		<span class="month">Jan</span>
	</a>

	

	<div class="entry">
		<p><strong>North Korea Erupts at &#8220;sordid hackwork by rubbish media&#8221;: Vows a &#8220;dear price the human scum and media&#8221;will &#8220;have to pay&#8221;</strong></p>
<p><em><strong>By Nate Thayer</strong></em></p>
<p>North Korea has erupted after months of silence over repeated news reports that Kim Jong-Un had plastic surgery to look like his grandfather, Kim Il Sung, with official media denouncing  &#8220;sordid&#8221; and &#8220;false report&#8230; released by enemies is a hideous criminal act which the party, state, army and people can never tolerate,&#8221; said Korean Central News Agency on Wednesday, calling it &#8220;sordid hackwork by rubbish media.&#8221;</p>
<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_811" style="width: 390px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjukis1.jpg"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-811" data-attachment-id="811" data-permalink="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/2013/01/24/north-korea-erupts-at-sordid-hackwork-by-rubbish-media-vows-a-dear-price-the-human-scum-and-mediawill-have-to-pay/kjukis1/" data-orig-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjukis1.jpg" data-orig-size="380,285" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-image-title="kjukis1" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjukis1.jpg?w=300" data-large-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjukis1.jpg?w=380" class="size-full wp-image-811" alt="Kim Il Sung (L) and his Grandson (R)" src="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjukis1.jpg?w=490" srcset="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjukis1.jpg 380w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjukis1.jpg?w=150 150w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjukis1.jpg?w=300 300w" sizes="(max-width: 380px) 100vw, 380px"   /></a><p id="caption-attachment-811" class="wp-caption-text">Kim Il Sung (L) and his Grandson (R)</p></div>
<p>What seemed to set Pyongyang off in a particularly virulent tizzy was not months of speculative South Korean news reports suggesting the young Kim had undergone plastic surgery, but rather a Chinese report last week by China&#8217;s Shenzhen TV who cited a diplomatic source who, on a private visit to Pyongyang, had spoken to a North Korean official who confirmed the plastic surgery rumours. KCNA referenced the Chinese report,</p>
<p>&#8220;Those hurting the dignity of the supreme leadership of the nation should not expect any mercy or leniency.</p>
<p>&#8220;Time will clearly show what dear price the human scum and media in the service of traitors of South Korea, slaves of capital, will have to pay,&#8221; it said.</p>
<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_812" style="width: 500px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjikishorse.jpg"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-812" data-attachment-id="812" data-permalink="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/2013/01/24/north-korea-erupts-at-sordid-hackwork-by-rubbish-media-vows-a-dear-price-the-human-scum-and-mediawill-have-to-pay/kjikishorse/" data-orig-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjikishorse.jpg" data-orig-size="940,627" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-image-title="kjikishorse" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjikishorse.jpg?w=300" data-large-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjikishorse.jpg?w=490" class="size-full wp-image-812" alt="Statues of Kim Il Sung and his son Kim Jong Il in Pyongyang" src="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjikishorse.jpg?w=490&#038;h=326" width="490" height="326" srcset="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjikishorse.jpg?w=490&amp;h=326 490w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjikishorse.jpg?w=150&amp;h=100 150w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjikishorse.jpg?w=300&amp;h=200 300w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjikishorse.jpg?w=768&amp;h=512 768w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjikishorse.jpg 940w" sizes="(max-width: 490px) 100vw, 490px" /></a><p id="caption-attachment-812" class="wp-caption-text">Statues of Kim Il Sung and his son Kim Jong Il in Pyongyang</p></div>
<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_813" style="width: 500px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjuhorse.jpg"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-813" data-attachment-id="813" data-permalink="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/2013/01/24/north-korea-erupts-at-sordid-hackwork-by-rubbish-media-vows-a-dear-price-the-human-scum-and-mediawill-have-to-pay/kjuhorse/" data-orig-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjuhorse.jpg" data-orig-size="993,586" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-image-title="kjuhorse" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjuhorse.jpg?w=300" data-large-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjuhorse.jpg?w=490" class="size-full wp-image-813" alt="Kim Jong Un on horse repeatedlly depicted in state media since he assumed power one year ago" src="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjuhorse.jpg?w=490&#038;h=289" width="490" height="289" srcset="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjuhorse.jpg?w=490&amp;h=289 490w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjuhorse.jpg?w=980&amp;h=578 980w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjuhorse.jpg?w=150&amp;h=89 150w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjuhorse.jpg?w=300&amp;h=177 300w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/kjuhorse.jpg?w=768&amp;h=453 768w" sizes="(max-width: 490px) 100vw, 490px" /></a><p id="caption-attachment-813" class="wp-caption-text">Kim Jong Un on horse repeatedlly depicted in state media since he assumed power one year ago</p></div>
<p>Apparently, Pyongyang issued a demarche to Beijing, and the Chinese ruling party instructed the official Chinese party organ, Xinhua, to debunk the stories, and Xinhua issued a report Tuesday, citing two of its correspondents in Pyongyang who  denied the plastic surgery rumours. Xinhua had its correspondents in Seoul and Pyongyang write a detailed background of the story which has circulated in the often gossip fueled and unverifiable rumor filled South Korean media, concluding that media stories that Kim Jong-un has had plastic surgery six times to resemble his grandfather was first reported in Seoul, then picked up by a Chinese news website, and then reported as fact on Shenzhen Satellite TV.</p>
<p>The rumours have been fed by Pyongyang’s propaganda apparatus who for months carefully crafted a meticulous written and pictorial narrative trying to evoke similarities between Kim Jong-Un and his grandfather, including through his dress, haircut, gestures and public appearances.</p>
<p>Xinhua cited as evidence of the stories falsehood that &#8220;There have been no news reports in North Korea about Kim Jong-un&#8217;s plastic surgery&#8221; and that there was &#8220;nothing suspicious&#8221; about Kim resembling his grandfather since they carry same genes.</p>
<p>While Kim tries to dress, walk and smile like his grandfather, this just aims to give the impression that he &#8220;holds the people dear,&#8221; Xinhua said.</p>
